    <title>The Innovation Race: Experimental Evidence on Advanced Technologies</title>
    <updated>2025-12-01T00:00:00+00:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>Zoë B. Cullen, Ester Faia, Elisa Guglielminetti, Ricardo Perez-Truglia &amp; Concetta Rondinelli</name>
